":113,"created_ts":1653275753,"created":"11:15:53","title":"落户大城市，还是保留农村的产权？","author":"Features","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Features","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0616/67df/560585_mini.png?m=1653275677"},{"id":854616,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>比如：\n我今天去舅舅家吃饭，待了不到半个小时（因为他家最近装修没地儿坐）就回来了。</p>\n<p>我个人一般看到这种表达方式会直接叉掉不看。\n不太喜欢的地方在于用（）来释义的地方明明可以用正常的逻辑表达清楚。\n却偏要选择这种不利于阅读的书写方式，所以有点理解不了为什么。</p>\n<p>如上面的例子：\n我今天去舅舅家吃饭，不过因为他家最近在装修没有地方坐所以待了半个小时就回来了。\n或：\n我今天去舅舅家吃饭，不过只待了半个小时就回来了，因为他家最近在装修没有地方坐。\n或其他....</p>\n<p>我觉得这种表达方式才是正常的以及利于阅读的，但加（）释义的方式却又很常见。</p>\n<p>所以你怎么看呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/854616","replies":98,"created_ts":1653269486,"created":"09:31:26","title":"你对发文/日常表达喜欢用（）来释义怎么看？","author":"james504","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/james504","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fb7fe79e1f66f5ad0a471ae83b45e23e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":854740,"node":"Blogger","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/blogger","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6974/ce5a/103_mini.png?m=1643940030","description":"<p>想看看持续输出的大佬们</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/854740","replies":91,"created_ts":1653295514,"created":"16:45:14","title":"能晒晒你的 Blog 么","author":"uilvn","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/uilvn","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5092/1e33/244331_mini.png?m=1508642591"},{"id":854704,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>感叹号屏、钛合金边框、4800 万像素后摄。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/854704","replies":89,"created_ts":1653286492,"created":"14:14:52","title":"有多少人有换 iPhone 14 Pro 的计划","author":"redr41n","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/redr41n","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cc3f/ce69/382970_mini.png?m=1632880998"},{"id":854601,"node":"奇思妙想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.co